description:
Blue Donut Studios is a UK based publisher of independent comics and software. First comic published was 'The Last Dead End' a 94 page horror graphic novel that was developed from an animation they had previously created.

Also of note is that they are developing comics using Augmented Reality within the comic pages as the printed issue and the version on Comixology shows.

The company has a range of forthcoming titles including a four part series entitled Blood & Valour: The Legends of Sir Bevis.
